le=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Offensive-Social-Media-Post-1.png?fit=214%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Offensive-Social-Media-Post-1.png?fit=731%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone  wp-image-596\" src=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Offensive-Social-Media-Post-1.png?resize=237%2C332&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"237\" height=\"332\" srcset=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Offensive-Social-Media-Post-1.png?w=1000&amp;ssl=1 1000w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Offensive-Social-Media-Post-1.png?resize=214%2C300&amp;ssl=1 214w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Offensive-Social-Media-Post-1.png?resize=768%2C1075&amp;ssl=1 768w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Offensive-Social-Media-Post-1.png?resize=731%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 731w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 237px) 100vw, 237px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" \/><\/p>\n<p>This card was buffed to 3. While it can hurt another player a lot, it also hurts to play it. A small buff makes it a bit better.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>Start Some Clubs<\/p>\n<p><img data-attachment-id=\"438\" data-permalink=\"https:\/\/jorgezhang.com\/2018\/07\/event-cards-next-steps\/start-some-clubs\/#main\" data-orig-file=\"https:\/\/i2.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Start-Some-Clubs.png?fit=240%2C336&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"240,336\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&